This is my personal Jenassa makeover.
Everything is standalone, beside the body (you will use what you have installed).
descriptionHtml:
[b]I've recently came back to some modding for Skyrim, so there will be an update with a new revamp of Jenassa.

DESCRIPTION:[/b]

This is my personal Jenassa makeover, and my first mod.
Everything is standalone, beside the body (you will use what you have installed).

Made her Essential.
Increased level cap to 60 and added Light Foot perk.

Face texture is based on UNP so you can get a little neckseam with a different body.
I could add a body to make it fully standalone, i will think about it...
